name: Cake Walk (Owenisalake)
description:
Note: Please use full screen for best experience

Link to my YouTube channel where I post weekly updates on the game: https://www.youtube.com/channel/

A simple game where you avoid new enemies at every level and try to survive the boss fights as well. 

This is currently in the beta phase and 32 of the 100 planned levels are out. Please leave feedback and suggestions because this is my first game and I really would appreciate the feedback. Leave feedback in the comments or send feedback to owenisalake@gmail.com.
